name: Who Dunnit? (fastest_mia, P1ayer0ne)
description:
Disaster has struck, the king of the land has been murdered! 

The city guard have brought you, the worlds greatest detective, in to help them solve the case. The city guard have provided you with full access to the murder scene to investigate the evidence and have interviewed each of the suspects for you. Its your job to put it all together and find out... Who Dunnit?

Programming and Design - Mia Kellet

Art and Design - Skylar Riches
